Heat the oil in a pan, add the garlic and sautÃ© for 1 minute.Stir in the peppers and the cherry tomatoes and heat for 2-3 minutes.Stir in the salami, beans and courgette and simmer gently for 6-8 minutes, stirring occasionally.Add the parsley and season, to taste, with salt and freshly ground black pepper. Transfer to a serving bowl and serve.